      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "不错，你我兄弟一场，拜托你给我捎个信儿，告诉江大哥今日之事，告诉他白涛、黑木二人已是朝廷的鹰犬了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣武士",
      "listener": "char_li_wen_cheng",
      "text": "李文成，你还要不要你的儿子？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣武士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，教你打吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "text": "萧大哥，你保护这孩子下山去吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "多谢恩公，我不跑！我爹爹不跑我也决不逃跑！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小兄弟，我助你一臂之力！李英雄，萧大哥，咱们并肩子杀下山吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "黑木大师",
      "listener": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "text": "小贼种，洒家超渡了你吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wen_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "李文成",
